replies.body:
My top 5 favorite animals:
Kiwis- they are cute, and unique. I have seen them a lot in the Zoo of Auckland, New Zealand.
Penguins- they are fluffy, silly, and cute creatures.
Dolphins- I love swimming, so when I was studying about the sea, ocean, etc, I learned about them and that is how it became one of my favorite animals.
Cats- they make an AWESOME pet and they are SOOOO cute
Doges- I am not a big fan of dogs, but if it is to choose a dog, it is doge. Mainly because of its' looks, and loyalty (correct me if I am wrong)
